{"tid":1288297,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"姜+蒜 能否治癌?","createTime":"2019-07-05T14:37:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T16:06:06.000Z","uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"745741a47a5ea402df7d082075ef9c2d08e6de26","tid":1288297,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T14:37:58.000Z","msg":"話說今日坐的士，遇到個的士佬講醫cancer經驗分享，傾起就聽到佢個偏方。<br />\n<br />\n事先聲明，此偏方乃是本人是道聽途說返來的，非經過嚴格科學驗證，但咁唔代表絕對無用，或無科學根據！詳見補充資料部分，有關姜黃素／大蒜素等等對癌細胞的作用有關的研究文獻。<br />\n<br />\n我絕對唔係盲目推荐什麽天然療法<br />\n不過如果西醫的化療＋電療＋手術＋標靶藥都醫唔好，而又仲返發，可以一試此方法！<br />\n反正cancer都仲算係不治之症，我見佢個方法低成本，低風險，可以一試，所以share下。<br />\n<br />\n至於食 姜+蒜 對治癌有無效果就睇大家運氣了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n李志堅先生所親口述分享的方法如下,<br />\n所需材料:<br />\n1. 將 黃肉火姜 切粒/切碎 泡於 九江雙蒸白酒中 (29%酒精), (泡愈久愈好).<br />\n2. 準備 生蒜頭<br />\n3. 口水<br />\n<br />\n服用方法:<br />\n每日飯後服用, 每日3-4次<br />\n1. 將 泡過酒的姜片 連同 生大蒜, 加上小量泡完姜的酒, 在口中慢慢咀嚼碎塊, 與口水混和, 讓口水中的酶與之產生作用. 然後才可吞服.<br />\n2. 正常服用後, 頭部會感到發熱, 食道, 胃部都會覺得發熱. 此乃正常現象, 因為姜和生大蒜是非常辣.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能的副作用:<br />\n1. 有可能會傷胃, 如胃部不適者要與胃藥一同服用.<br />\n2. 未吃慣的人, 姜和生大蒜是非常辣, 難入口. 但習慣後便會改善, 一開始可能食慢啲, 食少啲.<br />\n3. 食生大蒜會「壯陽」.<br />\n4. 此品含有高濃度酒精, 只能每次服食數茶匙, 不能多飲, 會醉!<br />\n(普通人的酒量亦未必夠高. 所以可按個人能力增加/減少酒精進食量.)<br />\n5. 提升心血管健康度, 降血脂, 膽固醇 blah blah blah<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n補充資料:<br />\n姜黄素 wiki:<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A7%9C%E9%BB%84%E7%B4%A0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25A7%259C%25E9%25BB%2584%25E7%25B4%25A0&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHajakGblTMbnvy6EODhsvCk%3D&h=aa0df790\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A7%9C%E9%BB%84%E7%B4%A0</a><br />\n大蒜素 wiki:<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A4%A7%E8%92%9C%E7%B4%A0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2592%259C%25E7%25B4%25A0&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHajakGblTMbnvy6EODhsvCk%3D&h=1faf14ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A4%A7%E8%92%9C%E7%B4%A0</a><br />\n<br />\n有關姜黄素(咖哩)殺癌細胞的 review:<br />\nCurcumin and Cancer Cells: How Many Ways Can Curry Kill Tumor Cells Selectively?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2758121/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC2758121%2F&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHajakGblTMbnvy6EODhsvCk%3D&h=367a2890\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2758121/</a><br />\n<br />\n天然食品致乳癌review<br />\nDietary Natural Products for Prevention and Treatment of Breast Cancer<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5537842/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC5537842%2F&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHajakGblTMbnvy6EODhsvCk%3D&h=d3684631\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5537842/</a><br />\n-&gt;其中談及到的ginger及garlic部分, 有興趣的巴絲可看裏面所引用的文獻"},{"pid":"7693f9a52b28aeb4ac8b7c3b58f367ebbc9b5510","tid":1288297,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T14:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5A7xTPa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5A7xTPa.png&h=9df1756d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/doNJ0uc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdoNJ0uc.png&h=f5c735e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n詳細方法可找李生/劉伯伯"},{"pid":"65d7d892e0e2abcbfd5ae2fd1f708911fb3900a9","tid":1288297,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T14:40:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n天然食品<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">防治</span></strong>乳癌review<br />\nDietary Natural P